        {
            "id": 6007170,
            "title": "意法半導體看好景氣回溫 但仍警惕地緣政治",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>歐洲半導體大廠意法半導體 (STMicroelectronics)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:STM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/STM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">STM-US</a>) 執行長謝利 (Jean-Marc Chery) 周三 (4 日) 在巴黎出席法國巴黎銀行 (BNP Paribas) 舉辦的活動時表示，公司近期已看到半導體市場景氣復甦的跡象，預計將在未來幾季推升業績表現，但同時對地緣政治風險仍保持謹慎。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007170%2Fl%2F13a8a746ab531dc6d1a8110545007343.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">意法半導體看好景氣回溫 但仍警惕地緣政治(圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>謝里指出，意法半導體目前第二季的訂單出貨比 (Book-to-Bill Ratio) 遠高於 1，顯示市場處於上行循環(Upcycle)，有利於未來營收成長。他強調，第二季至少可達到先前財測中值 27.1 億美元，並看好復甦勢頭至少將延續到第三季，屆時銷售額可望年增轉正。然而，他也坦言，地緣政治風險，特別是美國總統川普的貿易戰與關稅政策，可能對 2025 年後半年的市場發展帶來不確定性。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>面對市場對於潛在庫存囤積的疑慮，謝利則澄清，目前並未觀察到客戶有大量囤貨的現象，「我不否認這種情況可能存在，但我們並未發現明顯跡象。」他補充指出，雖然中國市場需求最為強勁，歐洲市場的需求依舊偏弱，顯示市場需求呈現區域性不均衡的態勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>意法半導體過去幾年深受車用、工業及個人電子產品市場疲軟的影響，導致訂單長期下滑，加上產能過剩與庫存壓力，整體市況低迷。然而，隨著 AI 和新興應用逐步帶動市場需求回升，半導體產業逐漸走出低谷。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至當地時間周三上午 11 點 52 分，意法半導體股價上漲 7.9%，領漲法國 CAC 40 指數及義大利 40 指數，反映投資人對市場復甦及公司營運展望的信心。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
